		<description><![CDATA[<p>We know it&#8217;s hard to believe, but students will be lining up at their lockers, in the cafeteria, and in the hallways here at Charles Wright before we know it. In the meantime, 2015-2016 start-of-school forms for Tarriers in all divisions—Lower School, Middle School, and Upper School—are now available online. Below are links to pages for each division that provide [&#8230;]</p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.charleswright.org/start-of-school-forms-for-2015-2016-are-now-available/">Start-of-School Forms for 2015-2016 Are Now Available</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="http://www.charleswright.org">Charles Wright Academy</a>.</p>
]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>We know it&#8217;s hard to believe, but students will be lining up at their lockers, in the cafeteria, and in the hallways here at <a href="http://charleswright.org/" target="_blank" data-cke-saved-href="http://charleswright.org">Charles Wright</a> before we know it. In the meantime, 2015-2016 start-of-school forms for Tarriers in all divisions—<a href="http://www.charleswright.org/resources/lower-school/" target="_blank">Lower School</a>, <a href="http://www.charleswright.org/resources/middle-school/" target="_blank">Middle School</a>, and <a href="http://www.charleswright.org/resources/upper-school/" target="_blank">Upper School</a>—are now available online. Below are links to pages for each division that provide letters from the heads of school, required registration and consent forms, optional forms, and additional information. Please read, sign, and return materials by August 3. (Please note that some forms are due August 17.) Think of it as parent summer reading!<span id="more-2035"></span></p>
<p><a href="http://www.charleswright.org/resources/lower-school/" target="_blank">Lower School Start-of-School Forms</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.charleswright.org/resources/middle-school/" target="_blank">Middle School Start-of-School Forms</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.charleswright.org/resources/upper-school/" target="_blank">Upper School Start-of-School Forms</a></p>
<p class="p1">For your convenience, most forms offer <a href="http://get.adobe.com/reader" target="_blank">Adobe Acrobat</a> fields in which to type information.</p>
<p><u><strong>*Please note that it is not possible to save your completed documents.*</strong></u></p>
<p><strong>Please be sure to print your completed documents before closing your browser. You are also welcome to print the forms, complete them by hand, and return them via mail to the school.</strong></p>
<p>Please call the front office of your child&#8217;s division with any questions: Lower School (253-620-8800), Middle School (253-620-8400), or Upper School (253-620-8300).</p>
<p>We look forward to seeing you in September!</p>
